{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Escape From Benjamin's Room</strong> is a unique 2D puzzle adventure that will put your brain to work. You play as a stranger trapped in an old scientist's room who has lost his wife and wants to bring her back to life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/h1.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think outside the box to solve all the puzzles in the room, click on any game objects to interact, and pay attention to the details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/h2.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Put your headphones on to get immersed in this incredible escape room game, you'll enjoy this adventure at best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/h3.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Besides the original Benjamin's room, you can play an Alternative room that has the same furniture, but different enigmas than the original room </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/h4.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you enjoy solving logic problems and playing adventures like escape rooms or puzzle games, you will enjoy this adventure and put your brain to work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/h5.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you get stuck on solving some riddle, click the bulb button to get a hint that will help you solve the current enigma and escape the room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027740/extras/xslogo2.png?t=1738161296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of\u00a0 <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Clock","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/2cfada7a0c12806b3dbeb9e0012dd5822f4a1992.jpg"},{"name":"Escape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/520932121249183f833ae31b1e0d2471dae81c74.jpg"},{"name":"The Globe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/dd0db2fc087ff4195d7e2dcdb3fbc3c397616632.jpg"},{"name":"The Hourglass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/f9c01d2b858e77202123540a1ebd9ce75a7c4300.jpg"},{"name":"The ink pen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/271c9a8dbc023e0dd08e2e00cb5acdaf4accef8b.jpg"},{"name":"The skull eye","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/a8df377d85784d36b71c2500829012b575493b05.jpg"},{"name":"The leaf","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3027740/5f1d45af995eb66eaee78556181f83597c8a3aa1.jpg"},{"name":"The Owl","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/